Oh, good. Cullen's here.

38
00:04:57,390 --> 00:04:59,432
Well, talk to you later.

39
00:05:22,456 --> 00:05:24,108
Happy birthday.
- Don't remind me.

40
00:05:24,208 --> 00:05:26,208
Mmm.

41
