49
00:05:48,858 --> 00:05:50,858
Uh-huh.

50
00:06:00,619 --> 00:06:03,169
We have to go to class.
- Okay.

51
00:06:07,793 --> 00:06:09,793
Wait a second.

52
00:06:10,254 --> 00:06:12,254
Someone wants you.

53
00:06:12,715 --> 00:06:14,715
Bella.
- Jacob.

54
00:06:15,134 --> 00:06:17,134
What?

55
00:06:18,137 --> 00:06:20,221
I'll leave you to talk.

56
00:06:24,435 --> 00:06:29,257
Hello, Biceps. You know, anabolic
steroids are really bad for you.

57
00:06:29,357 --> 00:06:31,634
Well, I’m just filling out, Bella.

58
00:06:31,734 --> 00:06:35,554
You know, it wouldn't seem so
drastic if we hung out more.

59
00:06:35,654 --> 00:06:38,516
You should switch schools.
You can come hang out with the palefaces.

60
00:06:38,616 --> 00:06:42,603
I’m all right.
I prefer the rez school's exclusivity.

61
00:06:42,703 --> 00:06:45,147
They let any old riffraff into this place.

62
00:06:45,247 --> 00:06:47,316
