Okay, what did you do?
- Hey.

802
01:09:48,861 --> 01:09:50,220
What did you do to him?
- Easy.

803
01:09:50,320 --> 01:09:51,346
He didn't want this.

804
01:09:51,446 --> 01:09:53,807
What did we do? What did he do?
What'd he tell you?

805
01:09:53,907 --> 01:09:55,309
Both of you calm down.
- Nothing.

806
01:09:55,409 --> 01:09:59,319
He tells me nothing because
he's scared of you.

807
01:10:03,625 --> 01:10:06,260
Too late now.
- Bella, get back.

808
01:10:06,753 --> 01:10:09,463
Paul, calm down, now.

809
01:10:18,098 --> 01:10:20,098
Bella.

810
01:10:20,601 --> 01:10:22,601
Run.

811
01:10:24,938 --> 01:10:26,938
Jake, run.

812
01:10:52,466 --> 01:10:54,466
Paul.

813
01:11:04,311 --> 01:11:07,541
Hey. Take Bella back to Emily's place.

814
01:11:08,649 --> 01:11:11,369
Guess the wolf's out of the bag.

815
01:11:16,073 --> 01:11:19,983
Alice, is it possible that everything is true?

816
01:11:20,661 --> 01:11:23,021
The fairy tales and horror stories?

817
01:11:23,121 --> 01:11:28,391
Is it possible that there isn't
anything sane or normal at all?

818
01:11:28,835 --> 01:11:30,737
Hey, l think we should go back
and see if Jacob's okay.

819
01:11:30,837 --> 01:11:33,448
l hope Paul sinks some teeth in him.
Serves him right.

820
01:11:33,548 --> 01:11:35,325
No way. Jacob's a natural.

821
01:11:35,425 --> 01:11:39,121
You see him phase on the fly?
l got five says Paul doesn't touch him.

822
01:11:39,221 --> 01:11:41,915
Come on in, Bella. We won't bite.

823
01:11:42,015 --> 01:11:44,015
Speak for yourself.

824
01:11:53,527 --> 01:11:58,797
Oh, hey, about Emily, Sam's fiancée?
Don't stare. It bugs Sam.

825
01:12:00,742 --> 01:12:02,436
Why would l stare?

826
01:12:02,536 --> 01:12:05,936
Are you guys hungry? Like l have to ask.

827
01:12:13,046 --> 01:12:14,615
Who's this?

828
01:12:14,715 --> 01:12:16,715
Bella Swan. Who else?

829
01:12:18,218 --> 01:12:19,244
Hmm.

830
01:12:19,344 --> 01:12:21,724
So, you're the vampire girl.

831
01:12:24,641 --> 01:12:26,766
So, you're the wolf girl.

832
01:12:29,563 --> 01:12:30,964
Guess so.

833
01:12:31,064 --> 01:12:33,649
Well, I’m engaged to one.

834
01:12:36,987 --> 01:12:41,532
Save some for your brothers.
And ladies first. Muffin?

835
01:12:42,576 --> 01:12:44,019
Sure. Thanks.

836
01:12:44,119 --> 01:12:48,315
Leave it to Jacob to find a
way around Sam's gag order.

837
01:12:48,415 --> 01:12:50,317
He didn't say anything to me.

838
01:12:50,417 --> 01:12:51,568
That's a wolf thing.

839
01:12:51,668 --> 01:12:54,154
Alpha's orders get obeyed
whether we want them to or not.

840
01:12:54,254 --> 01:12:56,490
And check it out.
We can hear each other's thoughts.

841
01:12:56,590 --> 01:13:00,661
