Wait, Jake, you can't.

872
01:15:15,061 --> 01:15:17,297
Don't worry. We can't touch
your little precious Cullen’s...

873
01:15:17,397 --> 01:15:20,287
...unless they violate the treaty.

874
01:15:20,400 --> 01:15:22,761
That's not what I’m saying.

875
01:15:22,861 --> 01:15:25,836
You can't kill vampires. They'll...

876
01:15:25,906 --> 01:15:27,641
They'll kill you.

877
01:15:27,741 --> 01:15:32,671
Really? We took out that leech
