880
01:15:39,920 --> 01:15:41,279
Victoria's here?

881
01:15:41,379 --> 01:15:44,366
Was. We chased her all the way to the
Canadian border the other night.

882
01:15:44,466 --> 01:15:47,869
She keeps coming back.
We don't know what she's after.

883
01:15:47,969 --> 01:15:49,969
l do.

884
01:15:52,682 --> 01:15:54,682
Me.

885
01:16:02,943 --> 01:16:06,346
Don't worry. We've got this place covered.

886
01:16:06,446 --> 01:16:09,336
She won't get near you or Charlie.

887
01:16:09,449 --> 01:16:11,184
Look, you've got to be careful.

888
01:16:11,284 --> 01:16:14,354
She's fast. You don't know how fast she is.

889
01:16:14,454 --> 01:16:19,639
You know, your lack of confidence
in us is a little insulting.

890
01:16:19,834 --> 01:16:22,129
All right, I’d better go.

891
01:16:23,088 --> 01:16:25,088
You gotta go?

892
01:16:25,549 --> 01:16:27,367
Yeah.

893
01:16:27,467 --> 01:16:29,593
Got a vampire to kill.

894
01:16:43,233 --> 01:16:45,776
Alice, I’m all right.

895
01:16:47,445 --> 01:16:49,445
Until I’m alone.

896
01:16:50,490 --> 01:16:53,210
And lately, that's all the time.

897
01:16:53,368 --> 01:16:56,062
Jacob's gone. He's hunting Victoria.

898
01:16:56,162 --> 01:16:58,398
And Charlie's hunting Jacob.

899
01:16:58,498 --> 01:17:00,498
And you're gone.

900
01:17:01,167 --> 01:17:03,167
And so is Edward.

901
01:17:06,923 --> 01:17:09,388
And there's just nothing now.

902
01:17:12,345 --> 01:17:14,470
You got something, Harry?

903
01:17:15,557 --> 01:17:17,557
Nope. Nothing.

904
01:17:24,858 --> 01:17:26,760
But l realize where l have to go,

905
01:17:26,860 --> 01:17:29,835
what l have to do to see him again.

