909
01:18:07,275 --> 01:18:10,778
...♫ With their frequency wires ♫...

910
01:18:18,203 --> 01:18:21,914
...♫ And you can do no wrong ♫...

911
01:18:28,213 --> 01:18:34,760
...♫ In my eyes ♫...

912
01:18:36,971 --> 01:18:40,474
...♫ You can do no wrong ♫...

913
01:18:46,731 --> 01:18:53,445
...♫ In my eyes ♫...

914
01:18:55,407 --> 01:18:57,434
...♫ A drunken salesman ♫...

915
01:18:57,534 --> 01:18:59,436
...♫ Your hearing damage ♫...

916
01:18:59,536 --> 01:19:01,396
...♫ Your mind is restless ♫...

917
01:19:01,496 --> 01:19:03,565
...♫ They say you're getting better ♫...

918
01:19:03,665 --> 01:19:07,320
...♫ But you don't feel any better ♫...

919
01:19:14,008 --> 01:19:16,036
...♫ Your speakers are blowing ♫...

920
01:19:16,136 --> 01:19:18,204
...♫ Your ears are wrecking ♫...

921
01:19:18,304 --> 01:19:20,206
...♫ Your hearing damage ♫...

922
01:19:20,306 --> 01:19:24,810
...♫ You wish you felt better ♫...

923
01:19:32,902 --> 01:19:36,655
...♫ You can do no wrong ♫...

924
01:19:42,829 --> 01:19:52,838
...♫ In my eyes ♫

925
01:20:27,373 --> 01:20:29,373
Don't do this.

926
01:20:33,880 --> 01:20:36,090
You wanted me to be human.

927
01:20:38,510 --> 01:20:40,510
Watch me.

928
01:20:42,597 --> 01:20:44,597
Please.

929
01:20:45,183 --> 01:20:46,167
For me.

930
01:20:46,267 --> 01:20:49,412
You won't stay with me any other way.

931
01:20:51,648 --> 01:20:53,648
Bella, please.

932
01:21:56,045 --> 01:22:02,467
♫ This constant noise all the time ♫...

933
01:22:12,937 --> 01:22:18,817
...♫ Even though you're
the only one l see ♫

934
01:22:21,779 --> 01:22:23,779
Breathe.

935
01:22:24,782 --> 01:22:26,782
Breathe.

936
01:22:27,493 --> 01:22:29,536
Come on, Bella, breathe.

937
01:22:36,628 --> 01:22:39,254
Bella? Bella, can you hear me?

938
01:22:45,595 --> 01:22:47,595
Jake?

939
01:22:48,389 --> 01:22:50,389
Come here.

940
01:22:55,188 --> 01:22:57,908
What the hell were you thinking?

941
01:22:58,691 --> 01:23:01,326
l just wanted to see something.

942
01:23:01,361 --> 01:23:06,376
Get her home. I’m gonna go help
out over at Harry's place.

943
01:23:08,076 --> 01:23:10,201
What happened at Harry's?

944
01:23:10,370 --> 01:23:13,430
Harry Clearwater had a heart attack.

945
01:23:13,706 --> 01:23:16,276
Charlie and my dad are over
at his place with his family.

946
01:23:16,376 --> 01:23:18,376
Is he okay?

947
01:23:20,046 --> 01:23:22,046
He's gone.

948
01:23:25,093 --> 01:23:29,853
Come on. I’ll get you something
dry and drive you home.

949
01:23:39,816 --> 01:23:42,401
108 degrees over here.

950
01:23:44,278 --> 01:23:46,278
God.

951
01:23:46,614 --> 01:23:48,614
