952
01:23:50,702 --> 01:23:53,479
It must be nice, never getting cold.

953
01:23:53,579 --> 01:23:55,579
It’s a wolf thing.

954
01:23:56,082 --> 01:23:58,082
It’s not.

955
01:23:58,084 --> 01:24:00,084
It’s a Jacob thing.

956
01:24:00,420 --> 01:24:02,420
You're just warm.

957
01:24:04,632 --> 01:24:06,757
You're like your own sun.

958
01:24:10,179 --> 01:24:13,890
