961
01:24:29,449 --> 01:24:31,449
Sam got angry.

962
01:24:31,951 --> 01:24:34,246
Lost it for a split second.

963
01:24:35,580 --> 01:24:37,790
Em was standing too close.

964
01:24:40,084 --> 01:24:43,314
He'll never be able to take that back.

965
01:24:45,423 --> 01:24:47,548
