966
01:24:58,895 --> 01:25:00,895
Sometimes,

967
01:25:02,940 --> 01:25:05,830
l feel like I’m gonna disappear.

968
01:25:12,075 --> 01:25:14,540
Okay, not that you need me...

969
01:25:14,994 --> 01:25:17,969
...to tell you something like this,

970
01:25:18,956 --> 01:25:23,121
but l always will.
You're not gonna lose yourself.

971
01:25:25,463 --> 01:25:27,758
l wouldn't let that happen.

972
01:25:29,884 --> 01:25:31,884
How?

973
01:25:34,597 --> 01:25:37,232
I’ll tell you all the time...

974
01:25:40,520 --> 01:25:42,521
...how special you are.

975
01:26:01,999 --> 01:26:04,209
Thank you. For everything.

976
01:26:11,259 --> 01:26:13,259
Wait.

977
01:26:15,221 --> 01:26:17,221
There's a vampire.

978
01:26:17,390 --> 01:26:19,250
How do you know?

979
01:26:19,350 --> 01:26:23,129
l can smell it. I’m getting you out of here.

980
01:26:23,229 --> 01:26:25,229
That's Carlisle's car.

981
01:26:26,315 --> 01:26:28,092
