982
01:26:28,192 --> 01:26:32,357
Bella, it's a trick. Stop.
You gotta come with me.

983
01:26:35,283 --> 01:26:36,893
They won't hurt me.

984
01:26:36,993 --> 01:26:40,730
lf a Cullen is back here,
this is their territory.

985
01:26:40,830 --> 01:26:43,232
Treaty says we can only
defend on our own lands.

986
01:26:43,332 --> 01:26:48,772
l can't protect you here.
- Okay. That's okay. You don't have to.

987
01:26:49,922 --> 01:26:51,657
You're about to cross a line.

988
01:26:51,757 --> 01:26:53,757
Then don't draw one.

989
01:26:53,968 --> 01:26:55,968
Please?

990
01:27:12,153 --> 01:27:13,554
Alice?

991
01:27:13,654 --> 01:27:16,629
Oh, my God. What are you...
- Bella.

992
01:27:16,866 --> 01:27:21,020
I’m sorry, l just, l can't
believe you're here. Is...

993
01:27:21,120 --> 01:27:25,066
Would you like to explain
to me how you're alive?

994
01:27:25,166 --> 01:27:26,192
What?

995
01:27:26,292 --> 01:27:30,202
l saw a vision of you. You jumped off a cliff.

996
01:27:30,421 --> 01:27:32,532
Why in the hell would you
try and kill yourself?

997
01:27:32,632 --> 01:27:33,741
l mean, what about Charlie?

998
01:27:33,841 --> 01:27:36,577
What about...
- l didn't try to kill myself.

999
01:27:36,677 --> 01:27:38,121
I was cliff jumping.

1000
01:27:38,221 --> 01:27:39,956
Recreationally.

1001
01:27:40,056 --> 01:27:42,056
It was fun.

1002
01:27:43,684 --> 01:27:48,869
l have never met anyone more prone
to life-threatening idiocy.

1003
01:27:53,194 --> 01:27:54,762
Does...

1004
01:27:54,862 --> 01:27:56,905
Did you tell him?

1005
01:27:56,989 --> 01:27:58,989
No.

1006
01:27:59,742 --> 01:28:03,057
He only calls in once every few months.

1007
01:28:04,080 --> 01:28:06,545
He said he wants to be alone.

1008
01:28:12,171 --> 01:28:15,826
Bella, what is that
God-awful wet dog smell?

1009
01:28:17,009 --> 01:28:18,744
Um...

1010
01:28:18,844 --> 01:28:20,844
That's probably me.

1011
01:28:21,597 --> 01:28:23,848
Or it's Jacob.

1012
01:28:25,101 --> 01:28:27,101
Jacob who?

1013
01:28:27,853 --> 01:28:30,148
Jacob's kind of a werewolf.

1014
01:28:31,565 --> 01:28:35,475
Bella. Werewolves are not
good company to keep.

1015
01:28:35,987 --> 01:28:37,987
Speak for yourself.

1016
01:28:42,702 --> 01:28:44,997
l had to see you were safe.

1017
01:28:46,414 --> 01:28:49,358
l thought you couldn't protect me here.

1018
01:28:49,458 --> 01:28:51,458
Guess l don't care.

1019
01:28:54,922 --> 01:28:57,557
Well, I’m not gonna hurt her.

1020
01:28:58,801 --> 01:29:00,703
No, you're just a harmless Cullen.

1021
01:29:00,803 --> 01:29:04,207
